topic.title: Hello ZeroNet, what's your favorite conspiracy theory, unsolved mystery, or creepy/unexplained thing?
topic.body:
Hello ZeroNet, what's your favorite conspiracy theory, unsolved mystery, or creepy/unexplained thing? (This could be something that happened to you personally, or just whatever.)

While I don't believe in most crazy conspiracy theories, although a few seem plausible, I find them very insteresting to learn about. What are your favorites? Do you have any suggestions for ones I should research?  
I'm planning on making a large compilation of all the popular ones.
